700209f-a.text:
(1)
1031 E. 172nd Street, north side, between Boone Avenue and West Farma Road, showing an old frame dwelling occupying the center of the block. The house, on the extreme right, is at the N.W.
corner of West Farms Road.
May 31, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The house, at a later date, seen from the opposite direction.
April 26, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
